===Etymology===
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*sreŋ||to live; to be alive; to give birth; raw; green}} (STEDT). May be an old dialect variant of {{och-l|青|green; blue}}. Also cognate with {{och-l|生|to live}}, {{och-l|性|nature}}, {{och-l|姓|surname}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

